description:
GEICO Mobile: Stunning. Simple. Smart.

Application supports all Apple devices.

Includes a comprehensive set of self-service functions to complete your insurance needs.

Policyholders:
*Access all your GEICO policies
*View full-screen digital ID cards
*Pay & manage your bills
*Get a quote to add, replace, or remove a vehicle
*View & manage your claims
*Submit claim and glass repair requests
*Chat with Lily, GEICO’s virtual assistant

Features for Everyone:
*Get Roadside Assistance without making a call
*Get guidance on collecting information during an incident using Accident Assistance

NOTE: To log into GEICO Mobile, your GEICO policy must:
*Be registered at www.geico.com
*Have an auto or motorcycle policy
*Not be subject to other policy restrictions
releaseNotes:
*Customize your experience by creating a profile for you and other drivers on your policy.
*Quickly make a payment with just a swipe of your finger.
*Roadside Help just got even better with features like interactive maps and live updates to confirm when your help will arrive. 
*Recently got an auto quote? You can now access recent quotes and even purchase a policy right from the app!
*Why wait? Contact Us now includes FAQ’s to get fast answers to your questions without having to make a phone call. 
*Attention to policyholders in Oklahoma, Ohio and South Dakota. You can now enjoy the awesomeness of using digital ID Cards! 
And more!
